{ This variation was first played approximately 150 years ago in a correspondence game between the City of Barmen and the Berlin Academy. }
1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. c3 Nf6 5. d4 exd4 6. b4
{ I would have liked to see the faces of the members of the City Berlin Academy when they found this move in their mailbox! }
6... Bb6 7. e5 d5 8. exf6 dxc4 9. b5 Na5 10. fxg7 Rg8 11. Qe2+ Be6 12. cxd4
